<p><a name="Software" id="Software"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Transport_Layer_Security&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Software">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Software</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/OpenSSL" title="OpenSSL">OpenSSL</a>: a free implementation (BSD license with some extensions)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/GnuTLS" title="GnuTLS">GnuTLS</a>: a free implementation (LGPL licensed)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/JSSE" title="JSSE" class="mw-redirect">JSSE</a>: a <a href="/wiki/Java_(programming_language)" title="Java (programming language)">Java</a> implementation included in the <a href="/wiki/Java_Runtime_Environment" title="Java Runtime Environment" class="mw-redirect">Java Runtime Environment</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Network_Security_Services" title="Network Security Services">Network Security Services</a> (NSS): <a href="/wiki/FIPS_140" title="FIPS 140">FIPS 140</a> validated open source library</li>
</ul>
